snippet.title: The Black Heart (PC) - ANANZI STORY MODE - Chapter 5 - Playthrough Gameplay Longplay
snippet.description:
Playing the Story Mode of The Black Heart (PC) as Ananzi.
The game is available for purchase on Steam. @TheBlackHeartVg #theblackheart #ikemen #indie

Chapter 5: The daughter of the prince
Ananzi is the daughter of the other world's prince, grandaughter of the murdered king;
She's intent on recovering the black heart for her father the prince to prove to him she is most trustworthy soldier and a relentless assassin.

Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL_YL558gxlL_ykkORnLODdW_qqKdwDNKq
